_sText: This map is based on the microsoft windows game Minesweeper, more visually than game mechanics wise. You can find the original gg_minesweeper HERE. The latest version of Minesweeper features the following additions/changes: - Custom .Nav by Chizbone - New and Dynamic layout (Red flagged boxes rise in the air for 30 sec when shot) - 32 Spawn-points - BUYZONES - HDR - 3D Skybox - Custom Radar Overlay - Updated skybox texture, made by Karate Kaefer. - Updated & additional custom textures, making for a more colorful map. - And More !! Throughout the map are 4 mini mines that you can use to reach the top of the boxes and the bordering ledge. Map is symmetrical to ensure balance. ENJOY!
